<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (lw tzwl ạlsmạ wạlạ̉rḍ wyạ ạljbạl wlạ klmh mn jlạlh trjʿ dạ ạ̉mr mḥạl)2
 1-(ạ̹dẖạ wʿd ywfy.ạ̹dẖạ lms ysẖfy wạ̉nạ ʿạysẖ fy kẖyrh dạ kẖyrh bykfy)2
 dạ kẖyrh bykfy
 2-(ạ̹dẖạ ạ̉mr ymsẖy w mʿạh mạ btʿbsẖ wạlkl qdạmh kẖạḍʿ wmstny)2
 kẖạḍʿ wmstny
 3-(yftḥ wlạ yqfl yqfl wạ̉mrh yṣyr wạ̹n mrh ytạ̉kẖr ʿlyạ klh ykwn llkẖyr)2
 klh ykwn llkẖyr
 4-(fy ạlnạr yʿdyny ʿ ạlmwj ymsẖyny wạ̹n qạmt ʿlyạ ḥrwb ynjyny)2
 ḥrwb ynjyny</lyrics>
